name: Le Chambon-sur-Lignon
context: I'm glad not to have to travel alone. Age 16, November 1941, Le Chambon-sur-Lignon, France. I'm in Le Chambon-sur-Lignon. It's way up on a high plateau in the mountains. It's beautiful here. What an amazing difference from Gurs! I'm staying at La Guespy, which is a home for refugees.
